name: SET 003
release_bio: WHY? Record Company brings yet another front to their recent onslaught of releases with SET 003 brought to you by whythough? and planned to be premiered on the WRPI radio station on March 13th, 2020. This mix features the best techno of the moment including WRC and WRC Blue Label favorites such as dyl_pykl, Katie Hoffstatter, M.A.T.Y.B., and over one hour of unreleased exclusives from label boss whythough?.
